# API Endpoints â€“ Book Model

## List All Books
GET /books/
- Returns a list of all books.
- No authentication required.

## Create Book
POST /books/
- Creates a new book.
- Authentication required.
- Required fields: title, author, published_date, isbn, pages.

## Retrieve Book by ID
GET /books/<id>/
- Returns details of a specific book.
- No authentication required.

## Update Book
PUT /books/<id>/
- Updates all fields of a book.
- Authentication required.

## Delete Book
DELETE /books/<id>/
- Deletes a book.
- Authentication required.

